nodes.text: Star Wars Galaxies: The Complete Guide: Prima Official Game Guide

Star Wars Galaxies: The Complete Guide: Prima Official Game Guide was a strategy guide published by Prima Games for Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided and its expansions Star Wars Galaxies: Rage of the Wookiees and Star Wars Galaxies: Trials of Obi-Wan, as well as the "New Game Enhancements" content.
